title: Percy Scown
text:
Percy Scown (13 July 1883 – 6 July 1966) was an <a href="Australian%20rules%20football">Australian rules football</a>er who played with <a href="Geelong%20Football%20Club">Geelong</a> in the <a href="Australian%20Football%20League">Victorian Football League</a> (VFL).
Notes.
